text: AwesomenessTV is a sketch comedy reality variety show created by Brian Robbins. It was based on the original YouTube comedy channel of the same name. it features comedy sketches from different actors, music videos, hidden camera pranks and various gags. It premiered on Nickelodeon in July 1, 2013 and ended on March 7, 2015. Category:Nickelodeon television series Category:2010s television series
title: AwesomenessTV (TV series)
